items.name: mango
items.description: Mango is a prototype package manager written in SwaziLang that acts as a reference implementation for Swazi’s future built-in package management system. It runs externally today, but its architecture and behavior are intentionally designed to mirror what the Swazi internal package manager will eventually provide natively inside the Swazi runtime.
